column5: Need to open a small area and then repaired after leak is fixed.  Thanks

I have a guy I've used at 2 of my homes that removed the stucco from the ceilings. Can't speak enough about him, Cleanest and best taper I've ever seen. He does weekends only, and you're in luck, as he's from your area. Check your pm.
Thanks is this the guy Mario at 416 . . .

Thanks,  Smokercrafty, he will come and see me! Sounds like a standup guy! Will chat on the weekend, he is 10 minutes away. So is smokercrafty because of the diesel fuel or do you cure the smoke problem Billm is a diesel guy, he only drives them I think, Misfish he is allaround good Newf (more Italian than me) guy. just ask what you need we are here and can help! That's fantastic news Ketchenany. He is definitely a man of his word. As for my screen name, it's because I own that model of boat. A 16.5' tinny that has seen a few lakes, and is just a bunch of fun to fish from. I thank you for your humbleness, and if anything arises, it's good to know you guys are here for advice, or whatever it may be. Let me know how things go. Take care.
